# STUB: Fake zeroclaw binary for local installer testing on OmniStation.
#
# Simulates the subset of the zeroclaw CLI that NemoClaw exercises:
#   --version            → prints stub version string
#   gateway start        → serves GET /health → {"status":"ok"} on port 42617
#   gateway get-paircode → prints a stub pair code
#   status [...]         → exits 0 (healthy)
#
